    "asOf": "2021-03-18",
    "date": "2021-05-06T13:10:47Z",
    "text": "School Reopening and Spending Transparency Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Education to establish and update monthly a public website to track state expenditures of certain COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) education relief funds. States must report on the operating status of their public elementary and secondary schools during the 2020-2021 school year for inclusion on the website."
